BP Southern Africa Names Derbesy as Chief Executive Officer

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-01T12:14:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/bp-southern-africa-names-derbesy-ceo-appoints-finance-operating-chiefs.html
BP Plc (BP/) ’s southern Africa unit
appointed Gerard Derbesy as its chief executive officer, the
London-based company said in an e-mailed statement today.  Derbesy, currently head of planning performance reporting
for refining and marketing, assumes his duties on Sept. 1, BP
said. BP’s southern African unit also named Priscillah Mabelane
as chief financial officer and Alph Ngapo as chief operating
officer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  